column2: "Hey, good work out there. What did you think of Biol Meduna's tentacles?"

"Oh, yes~
Doesn't that slimy feeling just make you shudder with delight?"

"Although, to be honest...
I won't be satisfied with just that."
"I want those tentacles to squeeze my body, to force themselves into my joints and pull me apart..."
"Ahh~! I want to play with more tentacles! There aren't enough enemies with tentacles!"
